modules/tasks/tasks.php
- Fixed issue with history table being populated simply when viewing tasks
- by creating/using a "peek" method which calls a modified version load()
- which does *not* go though the "updateDynamics" process. This "process"
- updates a dynamic tasks information and then stores the results back into
- the database ... even if a change never actually occurred.
- 
